<br>
Perhaps people are confusing dire charm with regular charm spells.<br>
<br>
Using our level 53 charm spell(boltrans) it would not be hard to get a hasted mob that quaded for 150. But you would be in signifagant danger when such a mob broke charm(damage done so fast a cleric cannot keep you healed). If you get stunned once you lose most of your health.<br>
<br>
All those people who think charm is overpowered should try regularly surviving a charm break on these mobs.<br>
<br>
